
<div class="text-center madlibs-header">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12 h3-fun">
      <h3 class="">Create your own Madlibs!</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12">
      <p>for the book:</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12">
      <h1>"<%= @book.title %>"</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




<p><%= flash[:error] %></p>
<form class="" action="/books/<%= @book.id %>/madlibs" method="post">
  <input
     name="authenticity_token"
     type="hidden"
     value="<%= form_authenticity_token %>">
     <input type="hidden" name="madlib[book_id]" value="<%= @book.id %>">
  <label for="title">Title:</label>
  <input type="text" name="madlib[title]" value=""><br />
  <label for="">Story:</label><br />
  <textarea type="text" name="madlib[story]" value="" rows="12" cols="40"></textarea>
  <input type="submit" name="" value="Create Madlib">
</form>

<p>Remember, you need to leave out some words.</p>
<p>Simply input the words you want to leave out like this:</p>
<p>_adj_ for adjective or _noun_ for noun.
